Shortmail,is,an,email,service,that,restricts,email,messages,to,characters,It,offers,features,like,Public,Conversations,no,attachments,and,better,integration,with,social,channels,The,Shortmail,API,gives,developers,programmatic,access,to,the,functionality,of,the,service,Methods,include,viewing,the,status,of,an,inbox,retrieving,messages,sending,mail,searching,for,messages,and,more,It,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,JSON